| **Functionary v3.2** | `>>>all` + `>>>${recipient}` | `>>>recipient` | `>>>name\njson` | None |
| **Kimi K2** | `<\|tool_calls_section_begin\|>` + `<\|tool_call_begin\|>` | Tool IDs: `functions.name:index` | Structured sections | `<think>...<\think>` |
| **LFM2** | `<\|tool_list_start\|>` + `<\|tool_list_end\|>` | `<\|tool_call_start\|>` | Python-style: `[name(args)]` | `<think>...<\think>` |
| **LFM2.5** | `List of tools: [` + NO `<\|tool_list_start\|>` | Plain text list | Python-style: `[name(args)]` | `<think>...<\think>` |
| **GigaChatV3** | `<\|role_sep\|>` + `<\|message_sep\|>` + NO `<\|function_call\|>` | Role/message separators | JSON objects | None |

